{"tid":1160300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<pubg> 有感而發  香港仲有幾多人玩","createTime":"2019-05-18T11:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T12:07:49.000Z","uid":242965,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76b218231161900ab4d19d422e4deafd78a60fde","tid":1160300,"uid":242965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我一直是個毒L，有玩下PUBG咁<br />\n但香港愈來愈少人玩，啲朋友唔係去apex就返去r6<br />\n慢慢，隊友都冇哂，得返自己一個<br />\n<br />\n其實一直都想打下訓練賽，睇見香港人打比賽打到去台灣打，真係好羨慕<br />\n香港可以話係零資源，佢地都咁有heart<br />\n<br />\n早幾日，喺dc群見到有條片<br />\n條撚樣又幾有心機剪片<br />\n主要係講啲細節野<br />\n仲有小小訪問咁去問個唔知係咪電莖損手既人<br />\n又唔係太悶喎，講既野又幾中重點<br />\n本身以為係啲小學雞show off果啲highight片<br />\n點知又唔係<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後，本身都有啲想搵game轉既我，又想下苦功打下pubg<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都睇過條片？ 都想玩返pubg??"},{"pid":"f71026c83745a9b8463e125965349226d69b40c1","tid":1160300,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"好多外掛狗, 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b649cb5bbf1dca81408a6911d989948901ccb70","tid":1160300,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"真心好撚好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f71bfbbd49fd5c86aa5f670d60fc6afee5181da","tid":1160300,"uid":163758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f71026c83745a9b8463e125965349226d69b40c1","tid":1160300,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"好多外掛狗, 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"好少喎, 對比apex"},{"pid":"04ad987adc7b0cb93781453dd5040b77e7b70671","tid":1160300,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"節奏慢 冇變化<br />\n點會維持到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而王者榮